name: Simple-admin

body:
### admin page...

## I am making a test admin panel for laravel 5.x

# in this case we can view the registered users in a specific route

my wesite is [this](http://haamid.ir)to contact me about project

type below line to download pack with composer :
`composer require hamid/simple-admin`

and go to this route :
`your.pro/admin`
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
